The paper proposes a novel technique to improve the training efficiency of neural networks, which is a common topic in the machine learning community. The proposed technique involves the combination of Batch Normalization and Dropout, which are widely used techniques in deep learning. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
